about.summary: A pipeline orchestration library executing tasks within one python session. It takes care of SQL table (de)materialization, caching and cache invalidation. Blob storage is supported as well for example for storing model files.

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pydiverse-pipedag" %}
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/pydiverse_pipedag-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f6456570522aac2c69267a0acf6f03ac8c63c78d4ab91ba143ef6b2f2e294291

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - poetry
    - pip
    - python >=3.6,<4.0
  run:
    - attrs >=22.1.0
    - msgpack-python >=1.0.4
    - networkx >=2.8.5
    - packaging >=21.3
    - pandas >=1.4.3,<2.0.0
    - prefect >=1.3,<3
    - pynng >=0.7.1
    - python >=3.8,<4.0
    - sqlalchemy >=1.4.39,<2.0.0
    - structlog >=22.1.0
    - tomli >=2.0.1
    - typing-extensions >=4.1.0,<5
    - python-box >=6.1.0

test:
  imports:
    - pydiverse.pipedag
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: None
  summary: A pipeline orchestration library executing tasks within one python session. It takes care of SQL table (de)materialization, caching and cache invalidation. Blob storage is supported as well for example for storing model files.
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file:
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - NMAC427
    - windiana42
